• Use base URL:
                                                         
  https://<your-domain> or http://<host>:4400            
                                                         
  All Excel routes are under:                            
                                                         
  /api/excel                                             
                                                         
  Headers                                                
  For almost all Excel endpoints:                        
                                                         
  - x-admin-api-key: <EXCEL_ADMIN_API_KEY> for template  
    generation and upload                                
  - x-user-id: <any-user-id> required for ownership/job  
    access                                               
  - Content-Type depends on endpoint                     
                                                         
  Auth behavior                                          
                                                         
  - Upload/template endpoints: admin only                
  - Job status/error download: owner or admin            
  - If you upload with x-user-id: alice, use the same x- 
    user-id later to fetch that job unless using admin   
    access                                               
                                                         
