  ## 2. Download preset template                         
                                                         
  GET /api/excel/template?type=student                   
                                                         
  Allowed type:                                          
                                                         
  - student                                              
  - placement                                            
  - other                                                
                                                         
  Headers                                                
                                                         
  - x-admin-api-key                                      
  - x-user-id                                            
                                                         
  Body                                                   
                                                         
  - none                                                 
                                                         
  Success response                                       
                                                         
  - Binary .xlsx download                                
  - Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-        
    officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet                   
                                                         
  Postman

  - Use Send and Download                                
                                                         
  Possible errors                                        
                                                         
  { "error": "Unknown template preset \"foo\"" }         
                                                         
